pred_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) AS cancelled_order_count FROM orders WHERE status = 'Cancelled' AND customerNumber IN (SELECT customerNumber FROM customers WHERE country = 'Norway') AND orderNumber IN (SELECT orderNumber FROM orderdetails GROUP BY orderNumber HAVING SUM(quantityOrdered * priceEach) > 50000);
